ransition-colors duration-300"> Audit Trail </h3> <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors duration-300"> Identity-aware audit records with queryable REST API. Caller, severity, and time range filters. Cloud-managed retention and search. </p> </div> <div class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 border border-zinc-800/50 hover:border-sky-500/20 hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-sky-500/5"> <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-sky-500/10 border-sky-500/20 border flex items-center justify-center text-sky-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500/20 transition-all duration-300"> <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.28m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-sky-50 transition-colors duration-300"> Behavioral Profiling </h3> <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors duration-300"> Network behavioral baselines, deviation detection, tool schema drift monitoring. Enterprise-grade runtime analysis. </p> </div> <div class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900/30 border border-zinc-800/50 hover:border-sky-500/20 hover:bg-zinc-900/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-sky-500/5"> <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-sky-500/10 border-sky-500/20 border flex items-center justify-center text-sky-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500/20 transition-all duration-300"> <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 7.5l-2.25-1.313M21 7.5v2.25m0-2.25l-2.25 1.313M3 7.5l2.25-1.313M3 7.5l2.25 1.313M