pan> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> </div> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32"> <div class="relative rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500/10 to-transparent border border-amber-500/20 p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden"> <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div> <div class="relative"> <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6"> <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/20 border border-amber-500/30 text-amber-400"> <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z"></path> </svg> </div> <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-100">
+ Security built into the proxy layer
+ </h2> </div> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8"> <div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3">Authentication</h3> <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400"> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>API keys with bcrypt hashing, prefix lookup, automatic expiration</span> </li> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>JWT/OIDC integration with JWKS validation and SSO support</span> </li> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>Identity propagation: track callers from HTTP header to audit log</span> </li> </ul> </div> <div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mb-3">Hardening</h3> <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400"> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>Agent TLS with custom CA and mTLS support</span> </li> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>Tool access filtering with allow/deny lists and glob patterns</span> </li> <li class="flex items-start gap-2"> <span class="text-amber-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span> <span>Capability declaration and runtime verification</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32"> <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
